songs.title: Here Today Gone Tomorrow
songs.lyrics:
Here today, gone tomorrow
Gonna like it baby, wanna drive you crazy
There I go

They say Rock n' Roll ain't here for long
They got another thing comin' till' it hits they won't know

In my mind I just don't follow
I believe in what I see through you
In my mind I hear the sound…

I feel what's real
I won't sell my act for one deal
I feel what's real, I'm gonna give it to you

Here today, gone tomorrow
Turn it up, play it loud
On the road, right now

I hear it round and round in my head
Gonna play the guitar, I'm gonna sing until I'm dead

In my mind I just don't follow
I believe this is the time
In my mind I hear the sound…

I feel what's real
I won't sell my act for one deal
I feel what's real, gonna give it to you

I feel what's real
I won't sell my act for one deal
I feel what's real, gonna give it to you darlin' right here
